'''''PHONE+''''' is a monthly trade publication for communication distribution channels providing news and strategic information to private-label resellers, agents, brokers, VARs, systems integrators, interconnects and dealers that deliver bundled voice, data, wireless, Internet and content services, and CPE. The magazine was established in 1987 and has a circulation of 20,000. The publication also is the sponsor of the Channel Partners Conference & Expo. It was published by [[Virgo Publishing]]'s Telecom Division,<ref>{{cite news|title=Virgo Publishing Acquires Billing & OSS World Magazine and Trade Show|url=http://www.prweb.com/releases/virgo/billingoss/prweb555567.htm|accessdate=4 February 2017|work=Prweb|date=24 September 2007|location=Phoenix}}</ref> based in [[Phoenix, Arizona|Phoenix]], [[Arizona]], U.S.A. Virgo was acquired by [[Informa]] in 2014.<ref>{{Cite news|author=Michael Rondon|title=Informa Acquires Virgo Publishing|work=Folio|accessdate=19 November 2014|date=30 July 2014|url=http://www.foliomag.com/2014/informa-acquires-virgo-publishing#.VGv3gMnimQ5}}</ref> Then the magazine was renamed as ''Channel Partners''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Craig Galbraith|url=https://www.linkedin.com/in/craig-galbraith-20743910|work=Linked In|accessdate=1 August 2016}}</ref>

